# === 💎 Inspiro AI · Git Ignore（最終穩定版）===
# 功能：保護金鑰、防止上傳暫存檔、確保 Railway 部署順暢
# 適用環境：GitHub + Railway

# === 📦 Node.js 套件暫存 ===
node_modules/
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*

# === 🔑 環境金鑰與機密設定（非常重要）===
.env
.env.*
*.key
*.pem
*.crt
*.cert
secrets/
keys/
private/

# === 🏗️ 編譯輸出或暫存檔 ===
dist/
build/
.cache/
.tmp/
out/
coverage/
*.tsbuildinfo

# === 🧠 Logs 與除錯檔 ===
*.log
logs/
debug.log
nohup.out
*.pid

# === 🖼️ 自動生成的圖片或檔案 ===
/generated/
public/generated/
uploads/
tmp_images/

# === ⚙️ 平台或部署設定檔（自動產生，無須上傳）===
railway.json
render.yaml
vercel.json
Dockerfile
.dockerignore

# === 💻 作業系統與編輯器雜項 ===
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
*.swo
*.bak
*.tmp

# === 🧪 測試相關（若未使用 Jest 可忽略）===
jest/
__tests__/
__mocks__/
coverage/

# === ✅ 強制保留這些檔案上傳到 GitHub ===
!package.json
!package-lock.json
!Procfile
!.nixpacks.toml
!server.js
!.env.example
!README.md
